{"word":"θάκημα","slug":"θάκημα","sections":[{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<el><b>θάκημα</b></el> <br/><b><a href='S:Etymology'>Etym.</a> </b>from <el>θᾱκέω</el>\n<el>(θάκημα, ατος, τό,) </el><p/><div class='li750'><b>1. </b><i>a sitting</i>, <a href='S:especially'>esp.</a> as a suppliant, <b><a href='S:Sophocles'>Soph.</a></b><p/></div><div class='li750'><b>2. </b><i>a seat</i>, <b><a href='S:Sophocles'>Soph.</a></b>, <b><a href='S:Euripides'>Eur.</a></b><p/></div>"}]}